        <text>
            <body>
                <p>
                    <persName key="d1e15087" xml:id="d1e141748">Dominus abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283933" xml:id="d1e141750" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame et Saint-Edme de Pontigny (1114 -)">Pontiniacensis</orgName>
                    </persName> testatur quod firma pax facta est inter dissidentes domos <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141753" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> et <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#280812" xml:id="d1e141756" corresp="abbaye de Quincy (1133 -)">Quinciaci</orgName> assensu
                    utriusque partis, abbatis scilicet<lb />
                    <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141760" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> et suorum
                    qui presentes erant, abbatis quoque <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#280812" xml:id="d1e141763" corresp="abbaye de Quincy (1133 -)">Quinciaci</orgName> et suorum qui fuerunt presentes, tali
                    conditione quod fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141767" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> in pasturis haberent totum nemus <lb />sine parte
                    alterius, et fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#280812" xml:id="d1e141772" corresp="abbaye de Quincy (1133 -)">Quinciaci</orgName> totum planum sine parte alterius. <persName key="d1e15093" xml:id="d1e141775">Milo, qui fuit abbas de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282300" xml:id="d1e141777" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Bouras ou Bonras (1119 -)">Burra</orgName>
                    </persName>, hoc idem dixit et super hoc addidit quod pasture de <lb />
                    <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324924" xml:id="d1e141781" corresp="Juvance">
                        <foreign>Juvenci</foreign>
                    </placeName> deberent esse in communi. <persName key="d1e15100" xml:id="d1e141786">Servius, qui tunc fuit prior <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#280812" xml:id="d1e141788" corresp="abbaye de Quincy (1133 -)">Quinciaci</orgName>
                    </persName>, dixit idem et addidit quod <persName key="d1e15106" xml:id="d1e141791">Milo monachus</persName>, qui est unus testium, fuit
                    judex pro uno <lb />abbate qui interesse non potuit assensu utriusque partis.
                        <persName key="d1e15112" xml:id="d1e141796">Hugo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324970" xml:id="d1e141798" corresp="Nehele">Nehele</placeName>, monachus
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#280812" xml:id="d1e141801" corresp="abbaye de Quincy (1133 -)">Quinciaci</orgName>
                    </persName>, totum hoc dixit. <persName key="d1e15118" xml:id="d1e141804">Nobertus conversus</persName> dixit hoc<lb />idem. <persName key="d1e15124" xml:id="d1e141810">Henscherus conversus</persName> dixit hoc idem. Isti sunt
                    testes ex parte abbatis <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#280812" xml:id="d1e141813" corresp="abbaye de Quincy (1133 -)">Quinciaci</orgName>. <figure type="pied-de-mouche" />
                    <persName key="d1e15130" xml:id="d1e141817">Abbas de Busseria</persName>, ex
                    parte abbatis <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e141820" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>, testa<lb break="no" />tur quod pax, que sero prelocuta
                    dicitur, omnino infecta fuit in crastino et dimissa, assensu utriusque partis et
                    presentibus duobus judicibus, <lb />
                    <persName key="d1e15137" xml:id="d1e141827">abbate scilicet <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283933" xml:id="d1e141829" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame et Saint-Edme de Pontigny (1114 -)">Poten.</orgName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e15143" xml:id="d1e141832">abbate de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282300" xml:id="d1e141834" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Bouras ou Bonras (1119 -)">Burra</orgName>
                    </persName>. <persName key="d1e15149" xml:id="d1e141837">Bernardus
                        monachus</persName> hoc idem dixit. <persName key="d1e15155" xml:id="d1e141840">Martinus conversus</persName> dixit idem. <persName key="d1e15161" xml:id="d1e141843">Ogerus conversus</persName> dixit idem.
                        <persName key="d1e15167" xml:id="d1e141847">Petrus conversus</persName>
                    <lb />dixit idem, excepto quod non cognovit judices, et ideo nescivit si
                    presentes essent.</p>
            </body>
